title: The Reporter Who Knew Too Much - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 9/16/20

description:
George Noory and legal analyst Mark Shaw discuss his investigation into the death of reporter Dorothy Kilgallen in 1965, and whether she was killed for reporting on the coverup of mob connections to the assassination of President John Kennedy.
